# Beyondx Salary Management System GitHub project
The project [bx-salary-ms](https://github.com/luffyke/bx-salary-ms)

## Clone Repository
$ git clone git://github.com/luffyke/bx-salary-ms.git

## Project Description
This is beyondx salary management system, it provides salary history, tax calculation, insurance calculation and work experience functions.

Development Language : PHP
Framework : CodeIgniter
Database : Mysql
HTTP Server : Apache

## Folders Description
\application
	\config - CI config
	\controllers - CI Controllers
	\views - Page Views
	\models - Object Models
	\hooks - ACL hook
	\libraries - Libraries
\js  - javascript
\css - css file
\sql - sql script
\xml - xml data